OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAndrew Giuliani, head of the White
OL,8,FHouse Task Force on the FIFA World Cup
OL,9,F2026 talks to ITV News Sports Editor
OL,10,FSteve Scott about security preparation
OL,11,Fand a potential showdown between Iran
OL,12,Fand the USA
OL,14,FA World Cup knockout tie between Iran
OL,15,Fand the United States would be "one
OL,16,Fheck of a storyline", Andrew Giuliani,
OL,17,FPresident Trump's World Cup tsar, has
OL,18,Ftold ITV News.
OL,26,@wD@`OUxD@TO]
