OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe director of the FIFA World Cup
OL,8,F2026 Task Force said every Iranian
OL,9,Fplayer had been issued with a Visa to
OL,10,Fenter the United States.
OL,12,F"They'll be invited to come in the day
OL,13,Fbefore the match, and we want to make
OL,14,Fsure that the team is safe. The team
OL,15,Fhas the opportunity to play," Giuliani
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"There are some officials that did not
OL,19,Fget their visas, and that was a very,
OL,20,Fvery clear decision."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@]O]zD@AOU|D@UO]
