OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIran's football federation has accused
OL,8,Fthe US of violating FIFA regulations.
OL,10,FThe Iranian team arrived in Mexico at
OL,11,Fthe weekend, after persuading FIFA to
OL,12,Fallow them to switch their training
OL,13,Fbase from Tucson, Arizona.
OL,15,FThe side will play their first of
OL,16,Fthree group games on the west coast of
OL,17,Fthe US on June 15, against New Zealand
OL,18,Fin Los Angeles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
