OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We want the team to be able to
OL,8,Fcompete", Giuliani said. "We want
OL,9,FIranian Americans to be able to enjoy
OL,10,Fthe team as well, and who knows what
OL,11,Flater round matchups could lead to."
OL,13,FIf the USA and Iran both finish second
OL,14,Fin their respective groups, they will
OL,15,Fmeet the day before American
OL,16,FIndependence Day, in Dallas.
OL,18,FThe presence of a country at war with
OL,19,Fthe host country is unprecedented in
OL,20,Fthe tournaments near 100-year-history.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@HO]pD@ZOUsD@dO]
