OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAsked whether a breakdown in the
OL,8,Fceasefire between the US and Iran
OL,9,Fwould impact Iran's presence at the
OL,10,Ftournament, Giuliani said: "Look, all
OL,11,FI can tell you is a dynamic situation.
OL,13,F"But the President has been consistent
OL,14,Fall along on this, going back to last
OL,15,Fyear, where he ended up granting an
OL,16,Fexecutive order for the team to be
OL,17,Fable to play.
OL,26,@rD@\OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
