OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"So, there's been no conversations
OL,8,Fabout the team not coming here to
OL,9,Fplay, and what I can tell you is the
OL,10,FPresident's been very consistent on
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FGiuliani, who is responsible for
OL,14,Fcoordinating security for all matches
OL,15,Fin America, revealed that terrorist
OL,16,Fdrone strikes were the biggest risk.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]
