OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It is a growing and emerging threat.
OL,8,FWe take it seriously every single day
OL,9,Fthat I've been on the job. And we've
OL,10,Fdone everything that we can to make
OL,11,Fthe sky safe around this World Cup."
OL,13,FGiuliani likened the security
OL,14,Foperation to hosting 78 Super Bowls in
OL,15,F39 days.
OL,17,F"If there are any incidents that go on
OL,18,Fat stadiums, we know that that,
OL,19,Funfortunately, is going to be the
OL,20,Fstory, and we want the story to be
OL,21,Fwhat happens on the field."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]yD@AOU}D@[O]
