OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAsked about exorbitant ticket prices,
OL,8,FGiuliani acknowledged costs were
OL,9,F'expensive'."
OL,11,F"Look, there's no doubt about it. The
OL,12,FPresident said it last week, or a
OL,13,Fcouple weeks ago, that tickets are
OL,14,Fvery expensive here.
OL,16,F"I think, honestly, that's what
OL,17,Fhappens when you end up getting a
OL,18,FWorld Cup, and you add the demand to
OL,19,Fcome to the United States of America.
OL,26,@qD@MO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
