OL,3,CIran v USA would be 'one heck of a
OL,4,Cstoryline', Trump's World Cup chief
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We've seen over six million tickets
OL,8,Fsold. The previous record was 3.5
OL,9,Fmillion tickets the last time the
OL,10,FWorld Cup was here. So it's just, you
OL,11,Fhave incredible demand for these
OL,12,Fgames, and it just drives up ticket
OL,13,Fprices."
